OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FEngland has beaten New Zealand by 115
OL,8,Fruns in the cricket to win the first
OL,9,FTest at Lord's.
OL,11,FGus Atkinson continued his love affair
OL,12,Fwith the grounds, wrapping up
OL,13,FEngland's 115-run victory over New
OL,14,FZealand in the first Rothesay Test
OL,15,Fwith yet another appearance on the
OL,16,Ffamous honours board.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
