PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FAtkinson took the last three wickets
OL,8,Fon day four to seal figures of five
OL,9,Ffor 30, his fourth five-for in just
OL,10,Fthree appearances to go alongside an
OL,11,Funexpected century in 2024.
OL,13,FThe Surrey seamer hurried the hosts
OL,14,Fover the line by sweeping aside
OL,15,Ftailenders Nathan Smith, Kyle Jamieson
OL,16,Fand Matt Henry, taking his Test record
OL,17,Fat the home of cricket to 26 wickets
OL,18,Fat just 9.5 apiece.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FThe result never looked in doubt
OL,8,Fdespite a counter-punching 44 not out
OL,9,Ffrom Glenn Phillips, with New Zealand
OL,10,Fall out for 138 chasing 254 on a sub-
OL,11,Fstandard batting surface.
OL,13,FThe win gets England back to winning
OL,14,Fways following their 4-1 Ashes
OL,15,Fthrashing in Australia, with Atkinson
OL,16,Fadding to strong performances from
OL,17,Fdebutant Emilio Gay and new-ball
OL,18,Fpartner Ollie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FGay's second-innings 57 was the
OL,8,Finnings of the match, the highest
OL,9,Fscore and longest innings on a
OL,10,Fbowler's paradise, while Robinson's
OL,11,Ffirst appearance in more than two
OL,12,Fyears yielded seven wickets.
OL,14,FNew Zealand's position was already
OL,15,Fperilous as they started out on 55 for
OL,16,Ffive, with any hopes built around
OL,17,Ftheir overnight pairing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
