PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FBoth have enjoyed memorable days at
OL,8,FLord's in the past, Devon Conway
OL,9,Fmaking a double century on debut five
OL,10,Fyears ago and Tom Blundell playing his
OL,11,Fpart in a 195-run stand in 2022.
OL,13,FBut conditions this week have been
OL,14,Fstacked firmly against the batters,
OL,15,Fand it took just a couple of minutes
OL,16,Ffor England to snare a sixth wicket.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
