OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FIt came in predictable fashion off
OL,8,FTongue's fourth delivery of the
OL,9,Fmorning, with significant seam
OL,10,Fmovement and low bounce proving a
OL,11,Flethal combination for Blundell. For
OL,12,Fthe 11th time in the match, the
OL,13,Fumpire's finger was raised for lbw.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
