PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FWith clinging on doing New Zealand no
OL,8,Ffavours, Phillips initiated a brisk
OL,9,Fgear change with three boundaries in
OL,10,Fseven deliveries. Better known for his
OL,11,Fwhite-ball game, Phillips' counter-
OL,12,Fattack injected some jeopardy with a
OL,13,Fstand of 53 coming off less than 12
OL,14,Fovers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
