FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FFor the first time, English eyes were
OL,8,Fbeginning to be drawn to the
OL,9,Fscoreboard, but it fell to Stokes to
OL,10,Fcalm any nerves. With two batting
OL,11,Ffailures and no first-innings wickets,
OL,12,Fthe captain was striving to make his
OL,13,Ffirst real mark on the game when he
OL,14,Fsquared up Conway and had him well
OL,15,Fcaught by Jacob Bethell at gully.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780909506
OL,3,CEngland beats New Zealand by 115 runs
OL,4,Cto win the first Rothesay Test at
OL,5,CLord's
OL,7,FWith that glimmer of resistance
OL,8,Fovercome, Atkinson topped up his
OL,9,Ffigures at the Pavilion End. Smith
OL,10,Flasted just three balls before edging
OL,11,Fbehind, and Jamieson lingered only
OL,12,Fslightly longer before flicking
OL,13,Fstraight to mid-wicket.
OL,15,FNeeding one more to secure his five-
OL,16,Ffor, Atkinson could not have wished
OL,17,Ffor a more willing opponent than
OL,18,FHenry, bowled for his second duck of
OL,19,Fthe match and the ninth in total.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
